                  <p>We can recover most types of cryptocurrency wallets, including:</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Bitcoin Core and other wallet.dat files</li>
                    <li>Ethereum JSON keystore files</li>
                    <li>Hardware wallets (Ledger, Trezor, KeepKey, etc.)</li>
