                    <li><strong>Partial seed phrases:</strong> 85-90% success rate (depending on available words)</li>
                    <li><strong>Hardware wallet recovery:</strong> ~92% success rate</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p class="mb-0">During the analysis phase of your recovery request, we'll provide you with a more accurate success probability specific to your case. If we determine that recovery is unlikely, we'll let you know before proceeding further.</p>
