              <div id="recoveryCollapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="recoveryHeading3" data-bs-parent="#recoveryAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>If we're unable to recover your wallet despite our best efforts:</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>For most services, you'll only be charged the initial analysis fee.</li>
                    <li>For contingency-based recovery services, you won't be charged the success fee.</li>
                    <li>We'll provide a detailed report explaining the recovery attempts made and why they were unsuccessful.</li>
                    <li>We may suggest alternative approaches or recommend specialized services for your specific case.</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p class="mb-0">Our goal is to be transparent about the recovery prospects. During the initial analysis, we'll provide you with a realistic assessment of the chances of success before proceeding with the full recovery process.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
