                <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#securityCollapse1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="securityCollapse1">
                  How do you ensure the security of my wallet information?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="securityCollapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="securityHeading1" data-bs-parent="#securityAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>We take security extremely seriously and implement multiple layers of protection:</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>All communications are encrypted using industry-standard TLS/SSL protocols.</li>
                    <li>Sensitive recovery work is performed in isolated, secure environments.</li>
                    <li>We follow strict access control policies with limited personnel access.</li>
                    <li>We never ask for complete private keys or seed phrases via email or chat.</li>
                    <li>All recovery specialists undergo background checks and sign comprehensive NDAs.</li>
                    <li>We utilize secure upload mechanisms for wallet files and related documents.</li>
                    <li>Customer data is purged after recovery is complete (typically within 30 days).</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p class="mb-0">Our security practices are regularly audited and continuously improved to maintain the highest standards of data protection and client confidentiality.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="securityHeading2">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#securityCollapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="securityCollapse2">
                  Do I need to share my private keys or seed phrase?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="securityCollapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="securityHeading2" data-bs-parent="#securityAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>Our approach to private information is carefully controlled:</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li><strong>In most cases, NO</strong> - our recovery techniques don't require your complete private keys or full seed phrase.</li>
                    <li>For password recoveries, we typically work with the encrypted wallet files directly.</li>
                    <li>For seed phrase recoveries, we usually only need the words you remember, not the complete phrase.</li>
                    <li>In certain specialized cases, secure sharing of private key information might be necessary, but this is done through our secure recovery portal only, never via email or chat.</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p class="mb-0"><strong>Important security note:</strong> We will NEVER ask you to share sensitive wallet information through unsecured channels like email or chat. Any such requests would be a sign of fraud and should be reported immediately.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="securityHeading3">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#securityCollapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="securityCollapse3">
                  What happens to my data after recovery is complete?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="securityCollapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="securityHeading3" data-bs-parent="#securityAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>After your recovery is complete:</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>All sensitive wallet files and recovery-related data are securely deleted from our systems within 30 days.</li>
                    <li>We use secure deletion methods that meet industry standards for data destruction.</li>
                    <li>Basic account information and transaction records are retained for legal and customer service purposes.</li>
                    <li>You can request immediate deletion of your data after successful recovery by contacting our support team.</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p class="mb-0">We recommend transferring your recovered assets to a new wallet with fresh credentials as soon as possible after recovery, as an additional security measure.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
